    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, honest condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with minor scratches, several small dings, and noticeable clear coat fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, the car is dependable for commuting, though it may require minor maintenance items in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at an affordable price point.",
