    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a history of fastidious ownership and rigorous adherence to maintenance protocols. Every aspect of this motorcar, from its pristine exterior finish to its flawless mechanical systems, remains in a state of absolute excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a benchmark example that delivers a driving experience indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to drive home your dream car? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014the paint is sparkling, the interior is spotless, and it still has that wonderful new-car smell. It runs perfectly and has been loved so much, but it's time for a new adventure. You seriously have to see this one in person to believe how pristine it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory-rated 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical state is peerless: the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis retains its original composure with fresh OEM bushings and Sachs dampers, providing the telepathic steering feedback these cars are known for. The exterior retains its factory depth with no swirl marks, while the Nappa leather interior shows no bolster wear. An absolute turn-key specimen for the purist collector.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. No accidents. Clean title.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true 'time capsule' specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive care. The exterior finish remains in showroom condition, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. It has been treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating and has remained strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover when not in use. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, bolsters are firm, and every electronic component\u2014from the navigation system to the ambient lighting\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder of every service record since day one, all performed by certified master technicians. Recent maintenance includes a preventative 30,000-mile service, a full fluid flush, and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires. This is an investment-grade vehicle for a discerning buyer who demands a car that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Includes both original keys, all manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
